description:
*Check out the cool new features including a pedigree chart!*
*Now works with Heredis files*
Got genealogy information? Like the free GenTree app for your webOS phone? GenTree HD is for you! Now designed specifically for your TouchPad, GenTree HD is a viewer for .ged (GEDCOM) files, a standard file format for genealogy information. Most genealogy software & websites can export a .ged file. Just load your .ged file on your TouchPad with the USB cable and GenTree HD can read it and display your information. Now you can carry your genealogy information with you wherever you go! 

Special characters not showing up? Try the preference setting for ANSI. That should do it for most! GenTree HD has been tested with file sizes up to 3MB, approximately 5800 individuals. But it should also work with even larger file sizes. If you run into any issues, please use the Help page to send us an email (or send one directly to support@jbgapps.com) so we can make GenTree HD work for you!
